                                       states, TMS has had extensive

                                       experience in meeting the demands

                                       placed on hospitals for uniform

                                       reporting under AHR-like laws.  TMS

                                       can readily apply this expertise in

                                       your health care facility.

     INSIDE RIGHT, SUBHEAD:            Summary of Systems Capabilities

     COPY:                                *Fully supports the recommended

                                       AHR functional chart of accounts

                                       while maintaining the current

                                       management reporting structure.

                                          *Accumulates and reports

                                       revenues, related standard units of

                                       measure. and cost allocation

                                       statistics by program service.

                                          *Reports salaries, wages, and

                                       related full-time equivalents (on

                                       the accrual basis) by natural

                                       classifications within functional

                                       cost center by productive and

                                       nonproductive hours and earnings.




